high_descs: Turn and go to the counter to the left of the sink in front of the pan sitting on the counter.
Pick up the knife that is in front of the pan on the counter.
With the knife in your hand turn and go to the table to the side where the fridge is.
Slice half the potato that is in front of the coffee pot on the table starting at the side closest to the coffee pot.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the fridge.
Place the knife to the left of the loaf of bread that is on the second shelf.
Turn and go to the table on the side where the fridge is.
Pick up the middle slice of potato.
With the potato in hand turn and go to the fridge.
Open fridge. Place slice of potato on the top shelf to the left of the lettuce.  Close fridge. Open fridge and grab the slice of potato on the top shelf to the left of lettuce.
With the potato slice in hand turn and go to the sink.
Place the potato slice in the sink in the front center.
anns.task_desc: Slice potato to put in fridge and sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go across the room.
Pick up the knife on the counter beside the large pot.
Turn around, head to the table, go left towards the wall and then turn right to the table.
Cut the potato on the table.
Turn right and then turn around and head to the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge to the left of the bread.
Turn right and go back to the table.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn around and go back to the fridge.
Put the slice of potato in the fridge to the left of the lettuce, close the fridge, open the fridge and pick the slice of potato back up.
Turn to the left and head to the sink.
Put the slice of potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of potato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left head to the counter
Pick up the bread knife on the counter beside the pan
Turn left then head to the left side of the round table
Slice the potato on the round table
Turn right head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in the knife then close it
Turn right then head to the left side of the round table
Pick up the slice potato on the table
Turn right head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the slice potato then close the fridge
Turn left head to the sink
Put in the slice potato in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled sliced potato in the sink
